Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.90,0:01:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想那兩個人誰會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.43,0:01:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道   他們實力在伯仲之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.00,0:02:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最理想的結果是雙方同歸於盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,省得我們麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望緋村能夠獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.74,0:02:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為新月村與煉獄的事做一了結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.41,0:02:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是如果四乃森贏了\N志志雄 你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.79,0:02:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時候   我就打倒四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是我成為最強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.86,0:02:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五十一話\N覺醒的時刻已到\N傷痕纍纍的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.74,0:02:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說我的心很脆弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.25,0:02:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.25,0:02:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莊面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.72,0:02:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,式尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.16,0:02:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對現在心靈極度脆弱的你而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是為了那四人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.76,0:03:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是以那四人為借口\N揮舞自己的兇劍而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.27,0:03:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住…住…住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.25,0:03:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會動怒否定\N是你下意識自覺到的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你瞭解什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.66,0:03:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少 我知道現在的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.36,0:03:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是以得到最強的稱號為幌子\N讓自我沉眠其中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.14,0:03:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃避現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.64,0:03:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不那麼想的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.21,0:03:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會因為害死那四人的\N自責念頭而崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我曉得的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使如此\N現在的你不論做任何事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那四人都不會高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.21,0:04:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被比自己還要強的男人\N責罵到內心深處的痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.08,0:04:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及不得不對一個敵人之外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.65,0:04:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己欣賞的男人\N非罵不可的那種痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.62,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去 每一擊都正中痛楚\N比剛才的廝殺還要痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫 你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 你把你的脆弱\N全部歸罪在那四人頭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使那四人成了惡靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.59,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫 你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.72,0:05:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番眾現在由小操在當頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護京都與御庭番眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.83,0:05:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她代替你拚命地\N在盡頭目的重任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.94,0:05:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操是堅強的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.27,0:05:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不樂見\N她與御庭番眾扯上關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.61,0:05:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我相信今後她自己一人\N可以做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.35,0:05:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我答應那堅強的女孩\N一定帶你回去時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.99,0:05:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管多麼堅強\N終歸是十六歲的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.83,0:05:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在各種苛刻的現實中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.90,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知做了多少努力\N讓自己振作起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.43,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠回報她那真實的淚水的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.14,0:06:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是說蒼紫你還不敢正視現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.31,0:06:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想得到最強的證據\N來當隱身的蓑衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以死來逃避嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.05,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快找回往日那堅強的心\N喚醒失去的尊嚴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.49,0:06:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是推動在\N觀柳邸停止的時間的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使如此 我還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.94,0:07:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必需給這場決鬥做個了結\N不然無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.28,0:07:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於給這場戰鬥做了結一事\N我沒有任何意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙哦 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.89,0:07:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的眼神跟剛才不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也頭一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.87,0:07:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那恐怕是比\N流落到觀柳邸更早以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.94,0:07:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翁大人所承認的\N以及那四人所尊敬的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操所仰慕的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.31,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,江戶城御庭番眾頭目\N四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論輸贏都沒有意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.75,0:07:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們最後的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只需使出…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全力！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.74,0:08:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是名副其實的\N劍心與蒼紫的最後決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.51,0:08:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫倒持二刀小太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.25,0:08:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無疑問會使出\N回轉劍舞.六連擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.65,0:08:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由左或右方使出的\N超高速六連擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是右方還是左方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.46,0:08:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對左右頸子已受傷的劍心而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.06,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一時的耽誤  一瞬的錯誤判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都會成為致命傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而劍心現在擺出拔刀姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不只會使出全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照那架勢來看應該會使出絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算蒼紫再強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.98,0:08:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到無法預測的新絕招攻擊\N他是必輸無疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.35,0:08:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也不能先出手\N這是完全的均衡狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.99,0:09:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莊面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,式尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.63,0:09:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到最後我才曉得\N自己嘴上說是為了你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.24,0:09:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是把誤入精神迷宮的\N自我的脆弱歸罪在你們頭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想瞞騙自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.88,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那很快就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是贏還是輸\N一切都會在這裏結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.62,0:09:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我一定要打贏 然後結束它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快無法呼吸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間恐怕連十分鐘都沒到\N感覺卻是這麼漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,均衡還沒有打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 這聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.65,0:10:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 這場戰鬥\N都會被報導到志志雄那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以使出絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.20,0:10:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.03,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 這場戰鬥\N都會被報導到志志雄那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以使出絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先下手為強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由左手發動攻擊\N瞄準目標是右頸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回轉劍舞六連擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活下去 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.39,0:11:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你就能自由自在\N使出天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.66,0:11:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不可輸給內在的斬人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.83,0:11:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是小惠與我\N大家都祈禱你平安無事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.61,0:11:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的就看我的心\N我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流奧義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.66,0:11:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人   由美打電報來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說緋村使出絕招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.91,0:12:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是蒼紫渾身解數的一擊\N能否擊中的瞬間拔刀術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詳細情況…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.52,0:12:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.06,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說沒有看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.86,0:12:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.07,0:12:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.24,0:12:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在蒼紫使出回轉劍舞後\N出招還能搶先蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說他的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.21,0:12:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是快得令人看不見的\N超神速拔刀術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 不只如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.69,0:12:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他應該還隱藏了什麼\N足以作為絕招的特性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.24,0:13:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只差那一點點呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.95,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好多的…一點點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.66,0:13:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時不行 超越痛楚的\N體內的感覺完全麻痹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.90,0:13:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是只有腦袋清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是格外清爽的的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的絕招是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.45,0:13:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是飛天御劍流的最終絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.75,0:14:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.29,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個絕招的威力確實強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.33,0:14:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 別太常用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種程度的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.77,0:14:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用一次 給予身體的負擔\N是其他絕招的好幾倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.47,0:14:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管多厲害的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.71,0:14:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦被敵人知道全貌\N那威力便會減掉一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.31,0:14:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道 謝謝你的忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.28,0:14:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我討厭機器   這樣就痛快多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.96,0:14:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 沒時間了 快趕路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.26,0:14:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧 我馬上也趕上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.14,0:14:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了   快帶我到下一個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.78,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說吧 左邊右邊 哪邊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.78,0:15:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是從左邊來的\N當然是右邊了 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.62,0:15:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼呀 老女人   你說什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莊面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火男…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.14,0:15:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,式尉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.55,0:15:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然沒得到最強的稱號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經盡全力戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.49,0:15:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他遵守約定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.33,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次換我回應他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾經對翁下手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還得看他們是不是肯原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.52,0:16:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是最強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.19,0:16:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 別離開崗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.86,0:16:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.23,0:16:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想辦法再撐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察一定會趕過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍耐到那時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.64,0:16:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道他們是不是真的能來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.89,0:16:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪…怪物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.00,0:17:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太不堪一擊了\N像在驅除老鼠一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.87,0:17:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 不二\N我們差不多該去葵屋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.48,0:17:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管別人了\N我們差不多該開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.05,0:17:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這姿勢是非常累人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別受她挑釁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.62,0:17:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道 可是這樣下去沒完沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.16,0:17:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了早點幫助大家\N我必需打倒這個敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.56,0:17:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜下來 小操\N他是十本刀的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.37,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能輕易舞動那種大鐮刀\N絕不是普通的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.41,0:17:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說我不是普通的女人\N講得好 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.18,0:17:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰是小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.28,0:17:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 可是你很可愛哦\N有充份的素質哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.05,0:17:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,素質？吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.19,0:17:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想以女色來蒙騙我明神禰彥\N你想得美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.03,0:18:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你比\N小操與啊薰漂亮也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 這個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.93,0:18:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 只講小操也就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說她比我漂亮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 這我可不服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.01,0:18:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連啊薰也…好過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 快道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我說的是實話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還可是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個鐮刀女人哪點好了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許她是有點可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.72,0:18:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我也…我也不輸她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.86,0:18:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操  冷靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.06,0:18:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我比這些小丫頭漂亮\N是理所當然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.30,0:18:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟 你好好修行\N可以有不錯成果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.27,0:18:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.37,0:18:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.61,0:18:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.17,0:18:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼修行\N男人也不可能變成女人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.68,0:18:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.48,0:18:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人不是鐮刀女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.08,0:18:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鐮刀男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我輸給一個男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.39,0:19:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 別說笑了 快來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.66,0:19:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正你活再久呀\N也不可能變得比我更漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.91,0:19:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜下來 現在衝過去\N等於正中他的下懷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.61,0:19:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰 不用管我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.68,0:19:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光靠小操一個  我不太放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.82,0:19:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 我去應付他\N你就跟小操聯手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.39,0:19:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我接受的不是讓我軟弱到無法\N自力戰鬥的三流修行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.03,0:19:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣就要相信自己的門生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.77,0:19:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二比一也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論男人女人\N這點禮讓我是無所謂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.71,0:19:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法\N此時只好照禰彥說的做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.98,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 現在我就相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.22,0:20:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是神谷活心流的嚴厲修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還有很多沒做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.92,0:20:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏躺下的話\N我絕不原諒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 要上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.85,0:20:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋 剛才你嘆息了\N別以為蒙面我就分不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.05,0:20:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然會想嘆息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.05,0:20:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好歹也是\N大名鼎鼎的十本刀之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然得應付區區一個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去聽說有個\N飛天御劍流的劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠以快如風的速度在天舞劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本人一直期待\N無論如何要跟他交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.57,0:20:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而今…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於志志雄大人命令來到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.41,0:21:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果竟是這情景  真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.64,0:21:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明神禰彥\N不是你所說的普通小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.88,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我年紀不大\N卻也親眼看過許多場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.59,0:21:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要與他交手的\N緋村劍心的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.49,0:21:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在距離劍心最近的地方\N看過最多場他的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.26,0:21:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我年紀小\N就對我不屑一顧的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想打倒劍心還早一百年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.07,0:21:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有辦法你就先從打倒我開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.54,0:21:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼你那麼急著想死的話 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.44,0:21:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是  我不會讓你輕鬆死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.25,0:21:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要讓你後悔\N剛剛不該侮辱我飛翔的蝙也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…難道是炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.89,0:21:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掛著那麼危險的東西 真是下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.56,0:21:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙  先前說了一堆大話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.03,0:21:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果卻幹這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.67,0:22:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本就是言行不一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑話 我又沒說要一彈殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.81,0:22:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.55,0:22:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是讓我飛起的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.02,0:22:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是十本刀\N飛翔的蝙也的戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.46,0:22:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛空發破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.39,0:22:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管武術到達多究極的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.56,0:22:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭頂是人類的絕對死角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.73,0:22:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對于飛在上空的敵人\N要反擊根本是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.63,0:22:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要讓你後悔不該侮辱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.64,0:22:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.11,0:22:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥

